MyBldrInpireLinkButton.label: Website Link
MyBldrInpireLinkButton.modal.title: Home Configure Website Link
MyBldrInpireLinkButton.modal.description: You’ve purchased a configurable Website link for this plan – smart move! Your prospective buyers will be able to explore the possibilities of the dream home they could build with you.
MyBldrInpireLinkButton.modal.text1: Be sure to copy your link and check below for detailed steps on what to do next.
MyBldrInpireLinkButton.modal.text2: You’ll need to take this link and add it to your website. Here are the typical locations other home builders have embedded this type of link:
MyBldrInpireLinkButton.modal.text3: Let your web visitors know you have an interactive experience waiting for them.
MyBldrInpireLinkButton.modal.text4: Do you have a page on your site dedicated to this plan? That is a great place to make the link available.
MyBldrInpireLinkButton.modal.description: Drive more interest to the configurable home with a custom image!
You can capture an image by clicking the Download button. The image can be used on your website, in your marketing materials, in a model home, or anywhere else you can think of!
MyBldrInpireLinkButton.modal.list1.text1: When a user clicks on the link, they will automatically open a new browser tab where Home Configure will open.
MyBldrInpireLinkButton.modal.list1.text2: From there, all of your web visitors can simultaneously create a custom design for themselves without affecting another visitor’s experience.
MyBldrInpireLinkButton.modal.list1.text3: They can also save and share their perfect design with their friends and family.
MyBldrInpireLinkButton.modal.list2.text1: Once you’ve sold this home plan, you’ll want your home buyer to lock in their specific design selections.
MyBldrInpireLinkButton.modal.list2.text2: Come back to this project and click the
button in the banner at the top. It’s that easy!
